nodes.text: Star Wars: The Rise of Kylo Ren

Star Wars: The Rise of Kylo Ren is a canon comic book miniseries written by Charles Soule and drawn by Will Sliney. The story explores the backstory of Kylo Ren and the Knights of Ren. The four-part series began on December 18, 2019.
